notes:
 Geophysical data for British Columbia can be obtained from three agencies:

1. BC Geological Survey: search the Publication Catalogue for released geophysical data and Assessment Reports for geophysical survey results from exploration activity;
2. Geological Survey of Canada: search GEOSCAN for geophysics in British Columbia and the Geoscience Data Repository for Geophysical Data;
3. Geoscience BC: has geophysical publications and data from surveys conducted since 2005.
